data.description: Welcome to your dream home on 2.18 acres of lush, agricultural-zoned land where the possibilities are endless! This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom oasis offers a unique blend of comfort, privacy, and open living spaces. As you enter, you'll be greeted by the inviting open concept design, flooded with an abundance of natural light that accentuates the spaciousness of the home. The high ceilings create an airy and luxurious atmosphere, perfect for both relaxation and entertaining. The semi-circular driveway leading up to the home not only adds to the curb appeal but also provides ample parking for you and your guests. Privacy is paramount, and the gated entrance ensures a tranquil and secure living environment. Whether you dream of cultivating your own crops, raising animals, or simply enjoying the serene surroundings, this property offers the space and freedom to make it your own. Approximately one acre surrounding the house is completely fenced in, offering a safe haven for your family and pets. Experience the joys of rural living without the constraints of HOA restrictions. Additionally, the home comes with a Jacuzzi, providing the perfect spot to unwind and soak in the beautiful surroundings. Schedule a viewing today and start envisioning the possibilities that await you in this charming and unrestricted slice of paradise.
